long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: ChatGPT is an artificial intelligence-powered search engine that provides natural language responses to questions. The ChatGPT response is displayed alongside Google search results, giving users the ability to quickly and easily compare the two sources of information. ChatGPT's response is displayed in a conversational format, allowing the user to interact with the AI in a natural way. This feature makes it easier for users to understand the information they are seeking and to identify the most accurate and relevant answer.
